### Get all users
GET {{host}}/shared/users?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get user by ID
GET {{host}}/shared/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create new user
POST {{host}}/shared/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "testuser",
  "password": "secret123",
  "name": "Test User",
  "role": "USER"
}

###

### Update user
PUT {{host}}/shared/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "role": "USER"
}

###

### Deactivate user
DELETE {{host}}/shared/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json